If I recall correctly:<br /><br /><ul><li><strong>Mode 0:</strong> four background layers</li><li><strong>Mode 1:</strong> three background layers, one rotates/scales</li><li><strong>Mode 2:</strong> two background layers, both rotate/scale</li></ul><br />While modes 3-5 are different bitmap modes. Somebody correct me if I'm wrong, but if I recall correctly that's the gist of it.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4526">Sik</a> — Sat May 23, 2015 8:57 am</p><hr />
